definition: this/these/(commonly pr. [zhei4] before a classifier, esp. in Beijing)
classifier indicating a small amount or small number greater than 1: some, a few, several

sentences.english: Among them, there was the herb Tuckahoe grown in Yunnan and Guizhou provinces.
sentences.chinese: 這些中藥中就有生長於雲南和貴州的茯苓。

sentences.english: All these writers run to sentiment.
sentences.chinese: 所有這些作家都有傷感的傾向。

sentences.english: The ICC must decide whether to indict the suspects.
sentences.chinese: 國際刑事法庭必須決定是否起訴這些嫌犯。

sentences.english: And those grownup who lose to a kid have the audacity to complaint?
sentences.chinese: 這些輸了的成年人還有臉抱怨？
這些勞累的孩子直到7點纔回家。

sentences.english: B:Here they are, will you weigh all our luggage together?
sentences.chinese: 這些都是，要不要把我的全部行李一起過磅？

sentences.english: A visit to one of these places is well worth while.
sentences.chinese: 這些地方的任何一處都是很值得一去的。

sentences.english: The sound of happy laughters called up memories of his childhood.
sentences.chinese: 這些歡笑聲使他回憶起童年時代。

sentences.english: The lines can include transformations and other sexiness.
sentences.chinese: 這些線可以包括轉換以及其它吸引眼球的東西。

sentences.english: So watch out for these tests because they happen all the time。
sentences.chinese: 所以，要當心這些測試，因爲它們無時不在。

sentences.english: What did these tattoos look like?
sentences.chinese: 這些紋身看起來像什麼？

sentences.english: These ignition wires send the charge to each spark plug.
sentences.chinese: 這些點火導線將電荷運送至每個火花塞。

sentences.english: All you have to do to win is unscramble the words here to find four names of birds.
sentences.chinese: 只要你能從這些單詞中找到四種鳥的名稱你就贏了。

sentences.english: But those justifications have an incontestable value in their own day.
sentences.chinese: 但是這些辯解在當時卻具有必要的意義。

sentences.english: The cases have been laboratory confirmed by the Institut Pasteur, Dakar.
sentences.chinese: 這些病例已得到達喀爾巴斯德研究所的實驗室確認。

sentences.english: The BLOs provide short-term shelter and can provide medical care.
sentences.chinese: 這些邊境聯絡處提供短期的庇護和醫療。

definition: this/this kind of/this sort of/this type of
every kind of/all kinds of/various kinds
regarding/as far as sth is concerned/with regards to
after all/all in all/when all is said and done/in the final analysis
to have sth to do with/to relate to/related to/to concern/concerning
only natural/as it should be/certainly/of course/without doubt
